            (WebKit::VisibleContentRectUpdateInfo::allowShrinkToFit):
            (WebKit::operator==):
            * UIProcess/API/Cocoa/WKWebView.mm: Add _allowsViewportShrinkToFit member variable,
            with getter and setter.
