            * UIProcess/ios/WebPageProxyIOS.mm:
            (WebKit::WebPageProxy::updateVisibleContentRects): Padd allowShrinkToFit to the web process via the VisibleContentRectUpdateInfo.
            * WebProcess/WebPage/WebPage.cpp:
