        Merge r187962. rdar://problem/21827815

    2015-08-05  Daniel Bates  <dabates@apple.com>

            REGRESSION (r185111): Clicking phone numbers doesn't prompt to call sometimes
            https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=147678
